caption.p: Functional analysis of differential lncRNAs. (A) Gene Ontology analysis heat map of co-expressed genes of differential lncRNAs. (B) Kyoto Encyclopedia of Genes and Genomes pathway analysis heat map of co-expressed genes of differential lncRNAs. lncRNA, long non-coding RNA; PPAR, peroxisome proliferator activated receptor; NOD, nucleotide-binding oligomerization domain-containing protein.
